videoSnippet.title: Hikaru Nakamura Beats a Super GM in 11 Moves
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Evgeny Bareev vs Hikaru Nakamura
Millionaire Chess (Blitz Tiebreaks B) (2015), Las Vegas USA, rd 3, Oct-11 
Queen Pawn Game: Zukertort Variation (D02)

1. Nf3 d5 2. d4 c6 3. Bf4 Qb6 4. b3 Nf6 5. e3 Nh5 6. Bg5 h6 7. Bh4 Nd7 8. Ne5 Ne5 9. Qh5 Ng4 10. Bg3 g6 11. Qh4 Bg7
